Feature: [U3] Unmark a book as favorite from catalog # src/features/u3_remove_favorite_book.feature:1

  Scenario Outline: User unmarks a favorite book -- @1.1                                                 # src/features/u3_remove_favorite_book.feature:13
    Given a book "Ormar på ett plan: En Python-berättelse" is already marked as favorite                 # src/features/steps/u3_remove_favorite_book_steps.py:7
    When the user toggles the heart icon for the favorite book "Ormar på ett plan: En Python-berättelse" # src/features/steps/u3_remove_favorite_book_steps.py:23
    Then the book "Ormar på ett plan: En Python-berättelse" is unmarked as favorite                      # src/features/steps/u3_remove_favorite_book_steps.py:29
    And the book "Ormar på ett plan: En Python-berättelse" is removed from My Books list                 # src/features/steps/u3_remove_favorite_book_steps.py:34
    And the favorite count in statistics is decreased by 1                                               # src/features/steps/u3_remove_favorite_book_steps.py:39

